[{"id": 426641, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2792, "text": "Uma surata que enviamos e prescrevemos, na qual revelamos l\u00facidos vers\u00edculos, a fim de que mediteis."}, {"id": 426642, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2793, "text": "Quanto \u00e0 ad\u00faltera e ao ad\u00faltero, vergastai-os com cem vergastadas, cada um; que a vossa compaix\u00e3o n\u00e3o vos demova decumprir a lei de Deus, se realmente credes em Deus e no Dia do Ju\u00edzo Final. Que uma parte dos fi\u00e9is testemunhe o castigo."}, {"id": 426643, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2794, "text": "O ad\u00faltero n\u00e3o poder\u00e1 casar-se, sen\u00e3o com uma ad\u00faltera ou uma id\u00f3latra; a ad\u00faltera n\u00e3o poder\u00e1 desposar sen\u00e3o umad\u00faltero ou um id\u00f3latra. Tais uni\u00f5es est\u00e3o vedadas aos fi\u00e9is."}, {"id": 426644, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2795, "text": "E \u00e0queles que difamarem as mulheres castas, sem apresentarem quatro testemunhas, infligi-lhes oitenta vergastadas enunca mais aceiteis os seus testemunhos, porque s\u00e3o depravados."}, {"id": 426645, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2796, "text": "Exceto aqueles que, depois disso, se arrependerem e se emendarem; sabei que Deus \u00e9 Indulgente, Misericordios\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426646, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2797, "text": "E aquele que difamar a sua esposa, em mais testemunhas do que eles pr\u00f3prios, que um deles jure quatro vezes por Deusque \u00e9 um dos verazes."}, {"id": 426647, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2798, "text": "E na quinta vez pedir\u00e1 que a maldi\u00e7\u00e3o de Deus caia sobre ele, se for perjuro."}, {"id": 426648, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2799, "text": "E ela se libertar\u00e1 do castigo, jurando quatro vezes por Deus que ele \u00e9 perjuro."}, {"id": 426649, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2800, "text": "E na quinta vez pedir\u00e1 a incid\u00eancia da abomina\u00e7\u00e3o de Deus sobre si mesma, se ele for um dos verazes."}, {"id": 426650, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 350, "ruku": 301, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2801, "text": "Se n\u00e3o fosse pela gra\u00e7a de Deus e pela Sua miseric\u00f3rdia para convosco... e Deus \u00e9 Remiss\u00f3rio, Prudent\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426651, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2802, "text": "Aqueles que lan\u00e7am a cal\u00fania, constituem uma legi\u00e3o entre v\u00f3s; n\u00e3o considereis isso coisa ruim para v\u00f3s; pelo contr\u00e1rio, \u00e9 at\u00e9 bom. Cada um deles receber\u00e1 o castigo merecido por seu delito, e quem os liderar sofrer\u00e1 um severo castigo."}, {"id": 426652, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2803, "text": "Por que, quando ouviram a acusa\u00e7\u00e3o, os fi\u00e9is, homens e mulheres, n\u00e3o pensaram bem de si mesmos e disseram: \u00c9 umacal\u00fania evidente?"}, {"id": 426653, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2804, "text": "Por que n\u00e3o apresentaram quatro testemunhas? Se n\u00e3o as apresentarem, ser\u00e3o caluniadores ante Deus."}, {"id": 426654, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2805, "text": "E se n\u00e3o fosse pela gra\u00e7a de Deus e pela Sua miseric\u00f3rdia para convosco, nesse mundo e no outro, haver-nos-iaa\u00e7oitado um severo castigo pelo que propalastes."}, {"id": 426655, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2806, "text": "Quando a receberdes em vossas l\u00ednguas, e dissestes com vossas bocas o que desconhec\u00edeis, considerando leve o que eragrav\u00edssimo ante Deus."}, {"id": 426656, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2807, "text": "Dever\u00edeis, ao ouvi-la, ter dito: N\u00e3o nos compete falar disso. Glorificado sejas! Essa \u00e9 uma grave cal\u00fania!"}, {"id": 426657, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2808, "text": "Deus vos exorta a que jamais reincidais em semelhante (falta), se sois fi\u00e9is."}, {"id": 426658, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2809, "text": "E Deus vos elucida os vers\u00edculos, porque \u00e9 Sapiente, Prudent\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426659, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2810, "text": "Sabei que aqueles que se comprazem em que a obscenidade se difunda entre os fi\u00e9is, sofrer\u00e3o um doloroso castigo, nestemundo e no outro; Deus sabe e v\u00f3s ignorais."}, {"id": 426660, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 351, "ruku": 302, "hizb_quarter": 140, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2811, "text": "E se n\u00e3o fosse pela gra\u00e7a de Deus e pela Sua miseric\u00f3rdia para convosco... e Deus \u00e9 Compassivo, Misericordios\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426661, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2812, "text": "\u00d3 fi\u00e9is, n\u00e3o sigais as pegadas de Satan\u00e1s; e saiba, quem segue as pegadas de Satan\u00e1s, que ele recomenda a obscenidadee o il\u00edcito. E se n\u00e3o fosse pela gra\u00e7a de Deus e pela Sua miseric\u00f3rdia para convosco, Ele jamais teria purificado nenhum dev\u00f3s; por\u00e9m, Deus purifica quem Lhe apraz, porque \u00e9 Oniouvinte, Sapient\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426662, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2813, "text": "Que os dignos e os opulentos, dentre v\u00f3s, jamais jurem n\u00e3o favorecerem seus parentes, os necessitados e expatriadospela causa de Deus; por\u00e9m, que os tolerem e os perdoem. N\u00e3o vos agradaria, por acaso, que Deus vos perdoasse? Ele \u00e9Indulgente, Misericordios\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426663, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2814, "text": "Em verdade, aqueles que difamarem as mulheres castas, inocentes e fi\u00e9is, ser\u00e3o malditos, neste mundo e no outro, esofrer\u00e3o um severo castigo."}, {"id": 426664, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2815, "text": "Dia vir\u00e1 em que suas l\u00ednguas, suas m\u00e3os e seus p\u00e9s testemunhar\u00e3o contra eles, pelo que houverem cometido."}, {"id": 426665, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2816, "text": "Nesse dia Deus os recompensar\u00e1 pelo que merecerem, e ent\u00e3o saber\u00e3o que Deus \u00e9 a verdade Manifesta."}, {"id": 426666, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 303, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2817, "text": "As despudoradas est\u00e3o destinadas aos despudorados, e os despudorados \u00e0s despudoradas; as pudicas aos pudicos e ospudicos \u00e0s pudicas. Estes \u00faltimos n\u00e3o ser\u00e3o afetados pelo que deles disserem; obter\u00e3o indulg\u00eancia e um magn\u00edfico sustento."}, {"id": 426667, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 352, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2818, "text": "\u00d3 fi\u00e9is, n\u00e3o entreis em casa de alguma al\u00e9m da vossa, a menos que pe\u00e7ais permiss\u00e3o e saudeis os seus moradores. Isso \u00e9prefer\u00edvel para v\u00f3s; qui\u00e7\u00e1, assim, mediteis."}, {"id": 426668, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 353, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2819, "text": "Por\u00e9m, se nelas n\u00e3o achardes ningu\u00e9m, n\u00e3o entreis, at\u00e9 que vo-lo tenham permiss\u00e3o. E se vos disserem: Retirai-vos!, atendei-os, ent\u00e3o; isso vos ser\u00e1 mais ben\u00e9fico. Sabei que Deus \u00e9 Sabedor de tudo quanto fazeis."}, {"id": 426669, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 353, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2820, "text": "N\u00e3o sereis recriminados se entrardes em casas desabitadas que tenham alguma utilidade para v\u00f3s; Deus sabe tanto o quemanifestais como o que ocultais."}, {"id": 426670, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 353, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2821, "text": "Dize aos fi\u00e9is que recatem os seus olhares e conservem seus pudores, porque isso \u00e9 mais ben\u00e9fico para eles; Deus est\u00e1bem inteirado de tudo quanto fazem."}, {"id": 426671, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 353, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2822, "text": "Dize \u00e0s fi\u00e9is que recatem os seus olhares, conservem os seus pudores e n\u00e3o mostrem os seus atrativos, al\u00e9m dos que (normalmente) aparecem; que cubram o colo com seus v\u00e9us e n\u00e3o mostrem os seus atrativos, a n\u00e3o ser aos seus esposos, seus pais, seus sogros, seus filhos, seus enteados, seus irm\u00e3os, seus sobrinhos, \u00e0s mulheres suas servas, seus criados isentasdas necessidades sexuais, ou \u00e0s crian\u00e7as que n\u00e3o discernem a nudez das mulheres; que n\u00e3o agitem os seus p\u00e9s, para que n\u00e3ochamem \u00e0 aten\u00e7\u00e3o sobre seus atrativos ocultos. \u00d3 fi\u00e9is, voltai-vos todos, arrependidos, a Deus, a fim de que vos salveis!"}, {"id": 426672, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 354, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2823, "text": "Casai os celibat\u00e1rios, dentre v\u00f3s, e tamb\u00e9m os virtuosos, dentre vossos servos e servas. Se forem pobres, Deus osenriquecer\u00e1 com Sua gra\u00e7a, porque \u00e9 Munificente, Sapient\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426673, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 354, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2824, "text": "Aqueles que n\u00e3o possuem recursos para casar-se, que se mantenham castos, at\u00e9 que Deus os enrique\u00e7a com a Sua gra\u00e7a. Quanto \u00e0queles, dentre vossos escravos e escravas, que vos pe\u00e7am a liberdade por escrito, concedei-lha, desde que osconsidereis dignos dela, e gratificai-os com uma parte dos bens com que Deus vos agraciou. N\u00e3o inciteis as vossas escravas\u00e0 prostitui\u00e7\u00e3o, para proporcionar-vos o gozo transit\u00f3rio da vida terrena, sendo que elas querem viver castamente. Mas sealgu\u00e9m as compelir, Deus as perdoar\u00e1 por terem sido compelidas, porque \u00e9 Indulgente, Misericordios\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426674, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 354, "ruku": 304, "hizb_quarter": 141, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2825, "text": "Temos-vos enviado vers\u00edculos l\u00facidos, e feito de exemplos daqueles que vos precederam, a uma exorta\u00e7\u00e3o para osdevotos."}, {"id": 426675, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 354, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2826, "text": "Deus \u00e9 a Luz dos c\u00e9us e da terra. O exemplo da Seu Luz \u00e9 como o de um nicho em que h\u00e1 uma candeia; esta est\u00e1 numrecipiente; e este \u00e9 como uma estrela brilhante, alimentada pelo azeite de uma \u00e1rvore bendita, a oliveira, que n\u00e3o \u00e9 orientalnem ocidental, cujo azeite brilha, ainda que n\u00e3o o toque o fogo. \u00c9 luz sobre luz! Deus conduz a Sua Luz at\u00e9 quem Lhe apraz. Deus d\u00e1 exemplos aos humanos, porque \u00e9 Onisciente."}, {"id": 426676, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 354, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2827, "text": "(Semelhante luz brilha) nos templos que Deus tem consentido sejam erigidos, para que neles seja celebrado o Seu nomee neles O glorifiquem de manh\u00e3 e \u00e0 tarde,"}, {"id": 426677, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2828, "text": "por homens a quem os neg\u00f3cios e as transa\u00e7\u00f5es n\u00e3o desviam da recorda\u00e7\u00e3o de Deus, nem da pr\u00e1tica da ora\u00e7\u00e3o, nem dopagamento do zakat. Temem o dia em que os cora\u00e7\u00f5es e os olhos se transformem,"}, {"id": 426678, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2829, "text": "para que Deus os recompense melhor pelo que tiveram feito, acrescentando-lhes de Sua gra\u00e7a; sabei que Deus agraciaimensuravelmente a quem Lhe apraz."}, {"id": 426679, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2830, "text": "Quanto aos incr\u00e9dulos, as suas a\u00e7\u00f5es s\u00e3o como uma miragem no deserto; o sedento crer\u00e1 ser \u00e1gua e, quando seaproximar dela, n\u00e3o encontrar\u00e1 coisa alguma. Por\u00e9m, ver\u00e1 ante ele Deus, que lhe pedir\u00e1 contas, porque Deus \u00e9 Expedito noc\u00f4mputo."}, {"id": 426680, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 305, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2831, "text": "Ou (estar\u00e1) como nas trevas de um profundo oceano, coberto por ondas; ondas, cobertas por nuvens escuras, que sesobrep\u00f5em umas \u00e0s outras; quando (o homem) estende a sua m\u00e3o, mal pode divis\u00e1-la. Pois a quem Deus n\u00e3o fornece luz, jamais a ter\u00e1."}, {"id": 426681, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2832, "text": "N\u00e3o reparas, acaso, em que tudo quanto h\u00e1 nos c\u00e9us e na terra glorifica a Deus, inclusive os p\u00e1ssaros, ao estenderem assuas asas? Cada um est\u00e1 ciente do seu (modo de) orar e louvar. E Deus \u00e9 Sabedor de tudo quanto fazem."}, {"id": 426682, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2833, "text": "A Deus pertence o reino dos c\u00e9us e da terra e a Deus ser\u00e1 o retorno."}, {"id": 426683, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 355, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2834, "text": "Porventura, n\u00e3o reparas em como Deus impulsiona as nuvens levemente? Ent\u00e3o as junta, e depois as acumula? N\u00e3o v\u00eas achuva manar do seio delas?, E que Ele envia massas (de nuvens) de granizo, com que atinge quem Lhe apraz, livrando delequem quer? Pouco falta para que o resplendor das centelhas lhes ofusque as vistas."}, {"id": 426684, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2835, "text": "Deus alterna a noite e o dia. Em verdade, nisto h\u00e1 uma li\u00e7\u00e3o para os sensatos."}, {"id": 426685, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2836, "text": "E Deus criou da \u00e1gua todos os animais; e entre eles h\u00e1 os r\u00e9pteis, os b\u00edpedes e os quadr\u00fapedes. Deus cria o que Lheapraz, porque Deus \u00e9 Onipotente."}, {"id": 426686, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2837, "text": "Temos revelado l\u00facidos vers\u00edculos; e Deus encaminha quem Lhe apraz \u00e0 senda reta."}, {"id": 426687, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2838, "text": "Dizem: Cremos em Deus e no Mensageiro, e obedecemos. Logo, depois disso, uma parte deles volta as costas, porquen\u00e3o \u00e9 fiel."}, {"id": 426688, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2839, "text": "E quando s\u00e3o convocados ante Deus e Seu Mensageiro, para que julguem entre eles, eis que um grupo deles desdenha."}, {"id": 426689, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2840, "text": "Por\u00e9m, se a raz\u00e3o est\u00e1 do lado deles, correm a ele, obedientes."}, {"id": 426690, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 306, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2841, "text": "Abrigam a morbidez em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es; duvidam eles, ou temem que Deus e Seu Mensageiro os defraudem? Qual! \u00c9 queeles s\u00e3o uns in\u00edquos!"}, {"id": 426691, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2842, "text": "A resposta dos fi\u00e9is, ao serem convocados ante Deus e Seu Mensageiro, para que julguem entre eles, ser\u00e1: Escutamos eobedecemos! E ser\u00e3o venturosos."}, {"id": 426692, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 142, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2843, "text": "Aqueles que obedecerem a Deus e ao Seu Mensageiro e temerem a Deus e a Ele se submeterem, ser\u00e3o os ganhadores!"}, {"id": 426693, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 356, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2844, "text": "Juraram solenemente por Deus que se tu lhes ordenasses (marcharem para o combate) iriam. Dize-lhes: N\u00e3o jureis! \u00c9prefer\u00edvel um obedi\u00eancia sincera. Sabei que Deus est\u00e1 bem inteirado de tudo quanto fazeis."}, {"id": 426694, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 357, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2845, "text": "Dize-lhes (mais): Obedecei a Deus e obedecei ao Mensageiro. Por\u00e9m, se vos recusardes, sabei que ele (o Mensageiro) \u00e9s\u00f3 respons\u00e1vel pelo que lhe est\u00e1 encomendado, assim como v\u00f3s sereis respons\u00e1veis pelo que vos est\u00e1 encomendado. Mas seobedecerdes, encaminhar-vos-eis, porque n\u00e3o incumbe ao Mensageiro mais do que a proclama\u00e7\u00e3o da l\u00facida Mensagem."}, {"id": 426695, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 357, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2846, "text": "Deus prometeu, \u00e0queles dentre v\u00f3s que cr\u00eaem e praticam o bem, faz\u00ea-los herdeiros da terra, como fez com os seusantepassados; consolidar-lhes a religi\u00e3o que escolheu para eles, e trocar a sua apreens\u00e3o por tranq\u00fcilidade - Que Meadorem e n\u00e3o Me associem a ningu\u00e9m! - Mas aqueles que, depois disto, renegarem, ser\u00e3o depravados."}, {"id": 426696, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 357, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2847, "text": "E observai a ora\u00e7\u00e3o, pagai o zakat e obedecei ao Mensageiro, para que tenha miseric\u00f3rdia de v\u00f3s."}, {"id": 426697, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 357, "ruku": 307, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2848, "text": "N\u00e3o penses (\u00f3 Mensageiro) que os incr\u00e9dulos podem desafiar-Nos na terra; a sua morada ser\u00e1 o inferno. Que funestodestino!"}, {"id": 426698, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 357, "ruku": 308, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2849, "text": "\u00d3 fi\u00e9is, que vossos criados e aqueles que ainda n\u00e3o alcan\u00e7aram a puberdade vos pe\u00e7am permiss\u00e3o (para vos abordar), em tr\u00eas ocasi\u00f5es: antes da ora\u00e7\u00e3o da alvorada; quando tirardes as vestes para a sesta; e depois da ora\u00e7\u00e3o da noite - tr\u00easocasi\u00f5es de vossa intimidade. Fora disto, n\u00e3o sereis, nem v\u00f3s, nem eles recriminados, se vos visitardes mutuamente. AssimDeus vos elucida os vers\u00edculos, porque \u00e9 Sapiente, Prudent\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426699, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 358, "ruku": 308, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2850, "text": "Quando as vossas crian\u00e7as tiverem alcan\u00e7ado a puberdade, que vos pe\u00e7am permiss\u00e3o, tal como o faziam os seuspredecessores. Assim Deus vos elucida os Seus vers\u00edculos, porque \u00e9 Sapiente, Prudent\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426700, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 358, "ruku": 308, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2851, "text": "Quanto \u00e0s idosas que n\u00e3o aspirarem ao matrim\u00f4nio, n\u00e3o ser\u00e3o recriminadas por se despojarem das suas vestimentasexteriores, n\u00e3o devendo, contudo exporem os seus atrativos. Por\u00e9m, se se abstiverem disso, ser\u00e1 melhor para elas. Sabei queDeus \u00e9 Oniouvinte, Sapient\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426701, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 358, "ruku": 308, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2852, "text": "N\u00e3o haver\u00e1 recrimina\u00e7\u00e3o se o cego, o coxo, o enfermo, v\u00f3s mesmos, comerdes em vossas casas, nas de vossos pais, devossas m\u00e3es, de vossos irm\u00e3os, nas de vossos tios paternos, de vossas tias paternas, de vossos tios maternos, de vossas tiasmaternas, nas de que tomais conta, ou na de vossos amigos. Tampouco sereis censurados de comerdes em comum ouseparadamente. Quando entrardes em uma casa, saudai-vos mutualmente com a sauda\u00e7\u00e3o bendita e af\u00e1vel, com refer\u00eancia aDeus. Assim, Ele vos elucida os Seus vers\u00edculos para que raciocineis."}, {"id": 426702, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 359, "ruku": 309, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2853, "text": "Somente s\u00e3o fi\u00e9is aqueles que cr\u00eaem em Deus e em Seu Mensageiro e os que, quando est\u00e3o reunidos com ele, para umassunto de a\u00e7\u00e3o coletiva, n\u00e3o se retiram sem antes haver-lhe pedido permiss\u00e3o. Aqueles que te pedirem permiss\u00e3o s\u00e3o osque cr\u00eaem em Deus e no Seu Mensageiro. Se te pedirem permiss\u00e3o para irem tratar de alguns dos seus afazeres, concede-a aquem quiseres, e implora, para eles, o perd\u00e3o de Deus, porque \u00e9 Indulgente, Misericordios\u00edssimo."}, {"id": 426703, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 359, "ruku": 309, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2854, "text": "N\u00e3o julgueis que a convoca\u00e7\u00e3o do Mensageiro, entre v\u00f3s, \u00e9 igual \u00e0 convoca\u00e7\u00e3o m\u00fatua entre v\u00f3s, pois Deus conheceaqueles que, dentre v\u00f3s, se esquivam furtivamente. Que temam, aqueles que desobedecem \u00e0s ordens do Mensageiro, que lhessobrevenha uma prova\u00e7\u00e3o ou lhes a\u00e7oite um doloroso castigo."}, {"id": 426704, "identifier": "pt.elhayek", "surah_number": 24, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0648\u0631", "surah_en_name": "An-Noor", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Light", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 18, "manzil": 4, "page": 359, "ruku": 309, "hizb_quarter": 143, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "pt", "name": "El-Hayek", "transelator_en_name": "Samir El-Hayek", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 2855, "text": "N\u00e3o \u00e9, acaso, certo, que \u00e9 de Deus tudo quanto h\u00e1 nos c\u00e9us e na terra? Sem d\u00favida que Ele conhece os vossossentimentos. E no dia em que (os humanos) retornarem a Ele, inteir\u00e1-los-\u00e1 de tudo quanto houverem feito, porque Deus \u00e9Onisciente."}]